XIST v0.4.3

This is a HTML generator/XML transformation engine/web publishing system
written in Python.

For documentation read xist/xsc.py.

The requirements for installing the package are Python 2.0b2 or
later, sgmlop from the Python XML package (available from
ftp://titan.bnbt.de/pub/livinglogic/xist/sgmlop.c or
from http://www.pythonware.com/products/xml/
(an older version)) and the Python Imaging Library
(available from http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/).

To compile everything, simply perform the following steps.

1) Run "python setup.py build" to copy *.py files.

2) To install everything in the site-packages directory as an xist/ package,
   run "python setup.py install".

If you have difficulties installing this software, send a problem report
to Walter Dörwald <walter@livinglogic.de> describing the problem.
